---
title: Speedy Cheesy Beef  Fusilli with Spinach and Crispy Shallots
description: This pasta dish combines old cheddar and Parmesan for the ultimate cheese factor! Wilted spinach is tossed into the mix for a healthy green bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fusillis-au-poulet-et-au-fromage-84769a72-e71ebb95.jpg
